---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="The story of VIANY.DIXON — island performance wear founded in Roatán by Viany Dixon.">
  <section class="px-5 sm:px-8 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-[900px] mx-auto">
      <p class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-bold mb-3 text-(--color-muted)">Our Story</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif italic text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-medium tracking-[-0.015em] leading-[1.05] mb-10">
        From the islands,<br/>for the world.
      </h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-[#444] leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg">
          VIANY.DIXON® was born from the way we live in Roatán. The Caribbean Sea decides our day —
          when we swim, what we wear, how we move from the beach to the boat to dinner without changing.
          Performance fabrics from the surf and dive worlds, designed with the precision of fashion.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every piece is engineered for sun, salt and movement: UPF 50+ certified swimwear and rashguards,
          structured trucker caps with the fish mark embroidered in the front, crystal slip-ons for the boardwalk,
          and signature accessories that travel anywhere.
        </p>
        <p>
          We design in Roatán. We make with conscious materials. We carry our island wherever we go.
        </p>
        <p class="font-serif italic text-xl mt-10">— Viany Dixon, Founder &amp; Designer</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
